'''Ivan Dimitrov Karayotov''' ({{lang-bg|Иван Димитров Карайотов}}) is a [[Bulgaria]]n [[archaeologist]] and [[historian]] who studied ancient and medieval archaeology and history.
Since 1972 he has worked at the Regional Museum of [[Burgas]].
